{@--1@} To fall,
fall down, come down, descend, drop
down, alight; {#avANmuKasyopari puzpavfzwiH#}
{#papAta vidyADarahastamuktA#} <ls>R. 2. 60</ls>;  
{#vfzwirBavane cAsya petuzI#} <ls n="R.">10. 77</ls>; ({#reRuH#}) 
